InternSpark Python Programming Internship Task 4:
# Flask Notes App

A simple Flask-based Notes Application developed as part of the **InternSpark Python Internship - Task 4**.

## 📌 Project Description

This application allows users to:

- Add notes
- Delete notes
- View all notes
- Use a clean Bootstrap interface

This project demonstrates Flask routing, HTML templates, and basic CRUD functionality.

---

## 🚀 Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Flask
- HTML5
- Bootstrap 5

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
flask-notes-app/
│
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
└── templates/
    └── index.html
```

---

## ▶️ Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/flask-notes-app.git
```

Go to the project folder

```bash
cd flask-notes-app
```

Install Flask

```bash
pip install flask
```

Run the application

```bash
python app.py
```

Open your browser

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

---

## ✨ Features

- Add Notes
- Delete Notes
- Flask Routing
- HTML Templates
- Bootstrap Responsive Design

